1
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:45,640
It's fine, Master.

2
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,360
We can't go to the hospital.

3
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:49,420
I can fix you up just by pressing on it.

4
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:50,600
Who am I?

5
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:52,400
I am Meng Wanfu.

6
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:55,050
I can definitely fix you up.

7
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:57,039
Don't worry, Master.

8
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:05,370
You'll definitely get better.

9
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:06,720
It's fine, Master.

10
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,800
Meng Wanfu.

11
00:02:20,720 --> 00:02:21,520
Take him away.

12
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:22,079
To the court?

13
00:02:22,079 --> 00:02:23,640
What court am I going to?

14
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:24,400
I'm not going to court.

15
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:24,760
Take the old man out.

16
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:25,640
I'm not going to court.

17
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:26,680
Father. Father.

18
00:02:26,680 --> 00:02:27,440
Cut the crap.

19
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:28,079
Father!

20
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:36,720
Father!

21
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:39,480
Father!

22
00:02:40,079 --> 00:02:41,240
You can't go over there.

23
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:42,440
Brother, this is my father.

24
00:02:42,440 --> 00:02:43,560
Please let me through.

25
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:45,220
Father, Father, it's Yujiao.

26
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,520
Father! Father!

27
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:47,480
You can't go over there. Father!

28
00:02:47,480 --> 00:02:49,079
Please, let me through.

29
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:51,720
Father! Father! Father!

30
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,000
Going to court means death.

31
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,400
Don't think I don't know.

32
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:55,920
The mute is digging a hole.

33
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:57,600
I'm not going to court. Shut up!

34
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:58,560
I'm not going to court.

35
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,160
I won't go to court. Hurry up.

36
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,240
I...

37
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,280
You're here.

38
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,600
Father! Father!

39
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,360
Father was carried away by them.

40
00:03:37,360 --> 00:03:39,040
Father was taken away by them.

41
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,400
Yunkui.

42
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:43,280
I found Brother Liao.

43
00:03:43,760 --> 00:03:45,640
He arranged it for us

44
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,960
and sent Father to the hospital.

45
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,040
Don't worry.

46
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,620
What I told you before,

47
00:03:55,640 --> 00:03:56,900
do you still remember?

48
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,280
Okay.

49
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,640
I brought you some clothes.

50
00:04:12,640 --> 00:04:13,800
Let's clean up

51
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,930
and go meet someone with me.

52
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:45,970
Brother Yunkui.

53
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,800
It's all a misunderstanding. A misunderstanding.

54
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,640
Have some tea.

55
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,240
Come, have some tea.

56
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:54,120
Yunkui,

57
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,360
I know you've

58
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,690
suffered a lot in there.

59
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,880
Just like when I first went to Director Lin's,

60
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:01,010
I had a hard time too.

61
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,280
What do they say?

62
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:04,080
No discord, no concord.

63
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:06,080
Right, Director Lin?

64
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,240
Yes, exactly.

65
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,770
No discord, no concord.

66
00:05:10,440 --> 00:05:11,640
I know Yunkui

67
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:14,320
has been determined from the start

68
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,880
to sacrifice for the Party-State,

69
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:17,080
just like me.

70
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:20,800
But it's not the final moment for sacrifice yet.

71
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:23,640
I

72
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,480
have already introduced to Yunkui

73
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,360
the path to save the country by indirect means.

74
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:29,400
I've also discussed it with Director Lin.

75
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:31,440
You will be the manager of this company,

76
00:05:31,440 --> 00:05:33,240
specifically representing me.

77
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,520
Mrs. Zhang.

78
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,250
Where did you receive your education?

79
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,880
Great China University.

80
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:43,200
As for Mr. Song Qingquan,

81
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:44,980
are you familiar with him?

82
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,620
Mr. Song is from the Chinese Department.

83
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:51,280
I attended his Introduction to Classics and Literature.

84
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:55,680
Mr. Song is a good friend of ours.

85
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:57,120
In that case,

86
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:59,240
we are all good friends now.

87
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,520
Come, make yourself at home.

88
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:01,600
Have some tea and snacks.

89
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:02,280
Thank you.

90
00:06:03,080 --> 00:06:05,720
Mr. Zhang, don't worry.

91
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,800
There's no risk in this company.

92
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,840
We just transport tung oil

93
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:11,160
from Chongqing

94
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:13,520
and ship quinine out of Shanghai.

95
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,160
That's all the business we do.

96
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:15,760
As for you,

97
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,960
you don't need to be responsible for the business operations.

98
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:18,680
Usually,

99
00:06:19,320 --> 00:06:20,840
just check the account books

100
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:22,400
and sign the bills.

101
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:25,200
There's nothing for you to worry about.

102
00:06:26,520 --> 00:06:27,600
Is that okay?

103
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,820
My father's health was ruined

104
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:39,120
in prison.

105
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:41,080
Until he is safe,

106
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,240
I can't agree to this.

107
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:46,400
Rest assured about that.

108
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:49,200
Your father is doing fine in the hospital.

109
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:50,300
How about this?

110
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,080
In a while,

111
00:06:51,080 --> 00:06:52,480
I'll send someone to take you there

112
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:53,400
to see him.

113
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,620
I'll take my leave.

114
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:11,840
Don't worry.

115
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,170
With me here,

116
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,720
he will definitely join.

117
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,200
Then,

118
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,280
let's arrange for him to stay at

119
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:22,000
the Secret Service Headquarters' staff dormitory.

120
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,600
It's also on Jessfield Road.

121
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:25,000
Surrounded by our own people,

122
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:26,200
so we can look after him.

123
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,920
Okay, I'll find someone right away

124
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,760
to contact Chongqing by radio.

125
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:32,940
I'll take my leave.

126
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:49,040
He is a general.

127
00:07:50,400 --> 00:07:51,840
But to me,

128
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,840
he looks like a cook.

129
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,680
But his wife

130
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:57,600
is quite interesting.

131
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:01,240
These two together

132
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,170
are really a strange combination.

133
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:04,520
What do you think?

134
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,800
What do you think?

135
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:12,930
It's not important.

136
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:15,040
Since that old fox Liao Fengnian

137
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,760
pushed him to the front,

138
00:08:17,400 --> 00:08:18,840
it means he is just a tile

139
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,120
in mahjong.

140
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,480
The 'Fa Cai' tile.

141
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:23,890
Use him if he can make money.

142
00:08:24,080 --> 00:08:25,440
Discard him if he can't.

143
00:08:26,080 --> 00:08:27,360
What's important now

144
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,660
is to establish a relationship with Chongqing.

145
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:33,840
Let's see if Liao Fengnian has the ability.

146
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:52,680
Doctor, how is my father?

147
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,880
The old man suffered a cerebral thrombosis

148
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,520
triggered by emotional agitation.

149
00:08:56,520 --> 00:08:57,780
What's more serious is

150
00:08:58,000 --> 00:08:59,280
that he has a history of stroke,

151
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,720
making his condition extremely critical.

152
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:03,080
Fortunately, he was brought to the hospital today.

153
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,400
We just gave him

154
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:05,760
an injection of antithrombotic drugs.

155
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:07,290
The patient has responded,

156
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:09,160
indicating he is improving.

157
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:10,040
Really?

158
00:09:11,600 --> 00:09:13,460
That's great. Thank you, doctor.

159
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,540
Don't thank me yet.

160
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:16,640
This drug is imported.

161
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,080
Not only is it expensive,

162
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:20,840
but our hospital only has a two or three-day supply.

163
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:21,560
Next,

164
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:23,480
you will have to buy it on the black market.

165
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:24,810
One course of treatment

166
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,680
costs about two small yellow croakers.

167
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:28,600
You have to figure it out yourselves.

168
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,440
I must inform you of this situation.

169
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,040
Okay.

170
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,320
Understood, doctor.

171
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,320
I'll leave now.

172
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,020
Thank you, doctor.

173
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,050
You're welcome.

174
00:09:57,840 --> 00:10:01,320
I can't work for that traitor company.

175
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:02,840
If Master wakes up

176
00:10:02,920 --> 00:10:03,880
and knows the truth,

177
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:05,760
he will definitely beat me to death.

178
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:06,720
I understand.

179
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:08,920
We are just stalling for time now.

180
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:10,640
Let's save Master first.

181
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,080
Besides, this is just

182
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:14,840
Liao Fengnian's wishful thinking.

183
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:16,680
We still don't know Chongqing's attitude.

184
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,200
As long as Chongqing doesn't nod,

185
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:19,600
no company can be opened.

186
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:20,680
I understand.

187
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:26,080
Liao Fengnian is sincere about saving Master.

188
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:27,880
But he doesn't want to get involved.

189
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:29,480
He really thinks so.

190
00:10:34,280 --> 00:10:34,800
Yujiao.

191
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,440
Liao.

192
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:36,680
How is Uncle?

193
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,200
The doctor said

194
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:40,930
his condition has stabilized after medication.

195
00:10:45,400 --> 00:10:48,320
Uncle, I am Fengnian.

196
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:53,520
Yunkui. Yueming.

197
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:56,600
Yunkui. Yueming.

198
00:10:58,040 --> 00:10:59,800
Yueming.

199
00:11:01,280 --> 00:11:02,800
Yueming.

200
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:06,440
A word, please.

201
00:11:15,560 --> 00:11:17,560
Chongqing replied to the telegram.

202
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,440
So fast.

203
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:22,780
What did it say?

204
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,120
Only four words.

205
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:27,560
Serve the country.

206
00:11:28,920 --> 00:11:30,200
Just as you expected.

207
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:34,720
Lin Changgeng isn't the only one who wants to make money.

208
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,160
Mr. Liao.

209
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:40,080
Although this is an expedient measure

210
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:42,160
you came up with to save Master,

211
00:11:42,160 --> 00:11:43,960
I still have to thank you.

212
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:47,680
But I must be clear up front.

213
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:49,080
Speak.

214
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:51,860
Helping Lin Changgeng means helping traitors.

215
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:54,040
I won't do it.

216
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:56,800
Once Master wakes up,

217
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:59,280
we have to find a way to leave.

218
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:01,920
What do you mean?

219
00:12:03,040 --> 00:12:05,240
Dumping me after using me?

220
00:12:05,560 --> 00:12:06,560
Burning bridges.

221
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:13,660
What's the situation?

222
00:12:13,760 --> 00:12:15,020
Where is your captain?

223
00:12:16,400 --> 00:12:18,480
Our captain is resting in the hospital gatehouse.

224
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,240
Do you want to see him?

225
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:19,920
No need.

226
00:12:20,280 --> 00:12:22,240
I just want to see if the hospital is safe.

227
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,680
Rest assured. It's safe.

228
00:12:23,840 --> 00:12:25,570
Okay, it's nothing. You can go.

229
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:29,490
Did you see that?

230
00:12:29,640 --> 00:12:30,840
Now let alone Uncle,

231
00:12:31,280 --> 00:12:32,160
even you

232
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:34,800
can't even step out of the hospital.

233
00:12:34,800 --> 00:12:36,920
Taking Uncle out of the hospital at this time,

234
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:37,760
isn't that just sending Uncle

235
00:12:37,760 --> 00:12:38,760
back to prison?

236
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:39,880
But Master's temper,

237
00:12:39,880 --> 00:12:41,480
it's not like you don't know.

238
00:12:41,760 --> 00:12:42,720
If he knew the truth,

239
00:12:42,720 --> 00:12:44,040
he would rather die in prison.

240
00:12:44,040 --> 00:12:46,480
Saving Uncle wasn't just a makeshift.

241
00:12:47,440 --> 00:12:48,600
What Uncle is like now,

242
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:50,060
you've all seen it, right?

243
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:52,800
Yes, I did talk to the hospital.

244
00:12:53,360 --> 00:12:53,840
But for this medicine,

245
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:55,080
we're relying on my dignity

246
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:56,010
to hold out here.

247
00:12:56,160 --> 00:12:57,960
How long my dignity can last,

248
00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,800
I don't even know myself.

249
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,240
And I tell you,

250
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:02,960
you doing this

251
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:05,440
is linked to Chongqing,

252
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:07,330
not some traitor like you said.

253
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,160
Of course.

254
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:16,800
As for you, if you insist on not doing it,

255
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:18,320
I won't force you.

256
00:13:18,880 --> 00:13:21,600
I'll find someone else for the company.

257
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:25,250
Mr. Liao, wait a minute.

258
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:30,240
I'll do it.

259
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:33,320
Yujiao.

260
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:36,560
Can I take this kid's words seriously?

261
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:38,760
Wanfu.

262
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,900
But I have one more condition.

263
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:43,520
Speak.

264
00:13:43,920 --> 00:13:44,720
To do this,

265
00:13:45,080 --> 00:13:47,480
we can't use our brigade commander's name.

266
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:49,160
Yunkui died for the country.

267
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:52,080
We indeed can't tarnish his reputation.

268
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:53,880
And you can't use my name either.

269
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:55,520
I am a dignified follower of Confucianism.

270
00:13:55,520 --> 00:13:57,250
I must save face for my parents.

271
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,360
You're just a commoner.

272
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,420
That name of yours.

273
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:00,760
And I told you,

274
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,160
we are just a shield.

275
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,660
Just play-acting, right?

276
00:14:03,680 --> 00:14:04,520
If you use your real name,

277
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:05,480
when others call you,

278
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:06,720
your reaction will be genuine, right?

279
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:08,240
Liao, you also said,

280
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:09,640
it's just a shield.

281
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:11,780
Why must we use a real name?

282
00:14:12,040 --> 00:14:13,640
Why must we use Zhang Yunkui?

283
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:15,420
Why must we use Meng Wanfu?

284
00:14:15,800 --> 00:14:18,080
Why must we adorn this fig leaf

285
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:19,600
with real names?

286
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:21,120
If you want it to roll off the tongue,

287
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:22,600
then call him He Bishi.

288
00:14:23,880 --> 00:14:24,600
Yujiao.

289
00:14:25,400 --> 00:14:26,530
These words of yours

290
00:14:27,680 --> 00:14:29,880
really slapped my face hard.

291
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:35,480
Buddy, your name is He Bishi.

292
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:38,160
I...

293
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:41,640
Am I not another He Bishi?

294
00:14:45,280 --> 00:14:46,340
Then it's settled.

295
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:48,000
I'll go report to Chongqing.

296
00:15:01,640 --> 00:15:02,400
Wanfu.

297
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:08,080
I'm sorry.

298
00:15:09,560 --> 00:15:11,600
Last time you took Yunkui's name,

299
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:15,440
it was to let you live.

300
00:15:16,640 --> 00:15:17,720
This time,

301
00:15:18,920 --> 00:15:20,640
I want to let Master live.

302
00:15:22,240 --> 00:15:25,920
But this name you're taking is a tarnished one.

303
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:27,720
Madam.

304
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:29,760
Master taught me in prison.

305
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:32,570
Leaving after the deed is done,

306
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:34,440
hiding one's identity and fame.

307
00:15:34,680 --> 00:15:36,320
Killing one person in ten steps,

308
00:15:36,320 --> 00:15:38,450
leaving no trace for a thousand miles.

309
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:40,010
You know what I mean?

310
00:15:42,240 --> 00:15:43,040
I understand.

311
00:15:43,920 --> 00:15:45,240
It's good to be educated.

312
00:15:45,240 --> 00:15:46,240
Look at this,

313
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:48,640
it didn't use our brigade commander's name,

314
00:15:48,640 --> 00:15:50,600
nor did it use my name.

315
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:53,000
It used the name you just mentioned,

316
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,320
He Bishi.

317
00:15:54,400 --> 00:15:56,400
Think about it. All the infamy

318
00:15:56,680 --> 00:15:58,340
falls on that guy surnamed He.

319
00:15:58,760 --> 00:16:00,240
It has nothing to do with us,

320
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:01,120
right?

321
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:04,160
Now,

322
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:07,400
we can only take it one step at a time.

323
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:11,370
When you're under someone's roof, you have to bow your head.

324
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:14,120
But as soon as Master gets well,

325
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:17,320
we have to find a way to make a clever escape

326
00:16:17,560 --> 00:16:19,420
and spread our wings and fly high.

327
00:16:19,520 --> 00:16:21,200
The clear blue sky cannot be deceived,

328
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:23,260
hiding one's achievements and fame.

329
00:16:23,800 --> 00:16:24,600
Right?

330
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:31,080
Right.

331
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:33,000
You've made

332
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:36,600
a lot of progress this year.

333
00:16:38,560 --> 00:16:39,760
Master taught well.

334
00:16:41,800 --> 00:16:42,040
Actually...

335
00:16:42,040 --> 00:16:43,100
I'll go see Father.

336
00:16:46,800 --> 00:16:48,360
That's the situation.

337
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:50,360
Everything happened so suddenly.

338
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:53,490
I really didn't have time to report to the organization.

339
00:16:53,640 --> 00:16:54,360
Yujiao,

340
00:16:54,760 --> 00:16:56,440
you don't need to blame yourself too much.

341
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:59,480
Mr. Zhang is the father of a hero.

342
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:02,840
Ensuring his safety is the right thing to do.

343
00:17:03,640 --> 00:17:05,500
Wanfu and I are already prepared.

344
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:07,040
As soon as we find a chance,

345
00:17:07,040 --> 00:17:08,900
we will figure out a way to escape.

346
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:10,640
There's no rush.

347
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:13,760
The Japanese control medicine and weapons

348
00:17:13,760 --> 00:17:15,160
so strictly.

349
00:17:15,319 --> 00:17:17,119
Then without a pass,

350
00:17:17,839 --> 00:17:20,800
not a single bullet can leave Shanghai.

351
00:17:21,359 --> 00:17:23,079
And what Lin Changgeng set up

352
00:17:23,079 --> 00:17:24,520
was a trading company.

353
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:27,240
His purpose is to use his privilege

354
00:17:28,119 --> 00:17:30,920
among the concession, Japanese-occupied areas,

355
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,120
and the great rear area to seek personal gain.

356
00:17:32,120 --> 00:17:33,240
Do you mean

357
00:17:33,680 --> 00:17:34,960
to use Lin Changgeng's company

358
00:17:34,960 --> 00:17:36,560
to work for the New Fourth Army?

359
00:17:36,560 --> 00:17:38,120
I just thought of it.

360
00:17:38,840 --> 00:17:40,700
I will report to the organization

361
00:17:40,880 --> 00:17:42,600
before deciding our next move.

362
00:17:42,600 --> 00:17:43,440
Okay.

363
00:17:45,280 --> 00:17:46,360
I'll be going then.

364
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:47,680
Stay safe.

365
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:02,040
Yueming.

366
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:04,600
The situation of the War of Resistance in 1941

367
00:18:04,600 --> 00:18:06,320
was extremely complicated.

368
00:18:07,040 --> 00:18:07,760
At the beginning of the year,

369
00:18:07,760 --> 00:18:08,840
KMT diehards

370
00:18:08,840 --> 00:18:10,520
initiated the New Fourth Army Incident,

371
00:18:10,520 --> 00:18:13,080
ambushing the Army Headquarters of the New Fourth Army ordered to move north,

372
00:18:13,080 --> 00:18:15,600
causing heavy casualties.

373
00:18:16,800 --> 00:18:17,560
Zhou Enlai

374
00:18:17,560 --> 00:18:20,560
wrote in tears and blood in Xinhua Daily,

375
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:23,200
"An unprecedented injustice,

376
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:25,120
a leaf in Jiangnan,

377
00:18:25,360 --> 00:18:26,880
infighting,

378
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:29,280
why torment each other."

379
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:32,680
The Central Committee of the Communist Party of China then

380
00:18:32,680 --> 00:18:34,800
rebuilt the Army Headquarters in Yancheng, Jiangsu,

381
00:18:34,800 --> 00:18:38,930
and continued to resist the Japanese north and south of the Yangtze River.

382
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:42,480
Your father Yunkui rushed to Central Jiangsu with worry,

383
00:18:42,840 --> 00:18:44,760
but saw with his own eyes that this army,

384
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:47,200
which had been announced to be disbanded,

385
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:49,680
took root in the soil of the people

386
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:53,040
and was reborn as the backbone of the War of Resistance.

387
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:57,680
Commander Zhang, this way.

388
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:04,840
China.

389
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:07,080
China.

390
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:09,360
China.

391
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:11,560
Commander Xie.

392
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:12,880
Commander Xie.

393
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:14,200
Over here. Over here.

394
00:19:14,520 --> 00:19:15,600
Look who's here.

395
00:19:20,320 --> 00:19:21,840
Yunkui.

396
00:19:22,000 --> 00:19:23,840
Yufeng, I came as promised.

397
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:25,560
I have been eagerly awaiting you,

398
00:19:25,560 --> 00:19:28,280
waiting so long for you, Yunkui.

399
00:19:28,600 --> 00:19:29,520
The men are all settled.

400
00:19:29,520 --> 00:19:30,200
Settled.

401
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:30,640
Good.

402
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:31,920
Yunkui, please come in.

403
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:32,600
Okay.

404
00:19:32,920 --> 00:19:34,240
Did everything go smoothly on the way here?

405
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,160
Of course.

406
00:19:35,440 --> 00:19:37,080
The New Fourth Army is better seen than heard of.

407
00:19:37,080 --> 00:19:38,960
The couriers are really resourceful

408
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:40,720
and can actually come and go freely

409
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:42,120
right under the enemy's nose.

410
00:19:42,120 --> 00:19:42,880
Yunkui, please take a seat.

411
00:19:42,880 --> 00:19:43,440
Okay.

412
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:46,160
It's pathetic to think about the enemy.

413
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:47,600
On someone else's land,

414
00:19:47,600 --> 00:19:48,880
they set up checkerboards

415
00:19:48,880 --> 00:19:49,720
and plum blossom poles,

416
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:52,240
but they just couldn't stop us.

417
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:55,680
Yufeng.

418
00:19:57,840 --> 00:19:59,800
I can't figure out the New Fourth Army Incident.

419
00:19:59,800 --> 00:20:00,960
The Japs

420
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,680
are tyrannical now,

421
00:20:02,840 --> 00:20:04,700
and our country is almost ruined.

422
00:20:05,080 --> 00:20:07,000
Instead of sharing a common hatred for the enemy and fighting the Japs,

423
00:20:07,000 --> 00:20:08,200
they want to fight a civil war.

424
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:09,530
Why torment each other?

425
00:20:10,040 --> 00:20:11,360
The April 12 Incident was like this.

426
00:20:11,360 --> 00:20:12,920
The Long March was like this too.

427
00:20:12,920 --> 00:20:14,720
Including the current New Fourth Army Incident,

428
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,380
it will only make us stronger.

429
00:20:16,600 --> 00:20:18,880
I believe what you have experienced

430
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:21,460
will only make you more united and stronger.

431
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:22,160
Report.

432
00:20:22,520 --> 00:20:24,380
Commander, the meeting is ready.

433
00:20:24,680 --> 00:20:25,480
Got it.

434
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:27,520
Yunkui,

435
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:29,120
I am really sorry.

436
00:20:29,440 --> 00:20:31,320
Ye Sheng and I have a meeting to attend.

437
00:20:31,320 --> 00:20:32,240
How about this?

438
00:20:32,600 --> 00:20:34,760
I'll send a guard to show you around.

439
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:37,130
We can talk in detail after my meeting.

440
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:38,000
No need to bother.

441
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,280
I'll just walk around by myself.

442
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:39,800
Okay.

443
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:41,600
Then please make yourself comfortable.

444
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:42,520
Make yourself at home.

445
00:20:42,520 --> 00:20:43,050
Alright.

446
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:43,880
Ye Sheng.

447
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:44,400
Yes.

448
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:46,520
Make yourself comfortable.

449
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:12,440
Liao found us a house

450
00:21:12,440 --> 00:21:14,480
in this alleyway.

451
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:16,920
Which way is it?

452
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:17,730
On the right.

453
00:21:19,480 --> 00:21:21,040
Do you have any food?

454
00:21:22,240 --> 00:21:23,700
Please, give me some food.

455
00:21:23,840 --> 00:21:25,880
Do you have any food?

456
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:28,040
This alleyway is quite lively.

457
00:21:28,200 --> 00:21:28,680
Yes.

458
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:31,040
It's very convenient here. Everything is available.

459
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:32,120
Turn left ahead.

460
00:21:33,040 --> 00:21:35,880
Please give me some food. Do you have any?

461
00:21:36,040 --> 00:21:36,960
Please give me some food.

462
00:21:36,960 --> 00:21:38,090
Do you have any food?

463
00:21:39,600 --> 00:21:42,040
That's mine.

464
00:21:42,040 --> 00:21:42,960
Give it to me.

465
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:46,960
That's mine.

466
00:21:47,240 --> 00:21:48,440
This pancake is mine.

467
00:21:48,520 --> 00:21:49,640
That's mine!

468
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:52,800
Shuyuan!

469
00:22:06,040 --> 00:22:09,000
Yunqi! Shuyuan!

470
00:22:14,840 --> 00:22:17,120
Yunqi!

471
00:22:17,320 --> 00:22:19,080
Yunqi, don't run.

472
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:20,520
Don't run.

473
00:22:20,760 --> 00:22:23,040
Yunqi!

474
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:26,720
My son!

475
00:22:36,280 --> 00:22:37,840
Come back!

476
00:22:38,360 --> 00:22:39,520
Uncle!

477
00:22:39,520 --> 00:22:40,600
Come back!

478
00:22:42,600 --> 00:22:45,200
I'm sorry.

479
00:22:47,680 --> 00:22:49,240
Come back!

480
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:53,520
Come back!

481
00:23:01,160 --> 00:23:05,600
I can't come back.

482
00:23:48,800 --> 00:23:50,040
Yunqi!

483
00:24:42,280 --> 00:24:43,000
Hurry up.

484
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:43,560
Coming.

485
00:24:43,760 --> 00:24:45,880
I told you to wind the yarn at home.

486
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:47,250
Hurry up.

487
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:49,560
Hurry up.

488
00:24:49,640 --> 00:24:50,280
Come on.

489
00:24:51,120 --> 00:24:51,640
Come on.

490
00:24:53,080 --> 00:24:53,840
Pull hard.

491
00:25:00,360 --> 00:25:01,690
Wind it a few more times.

492
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:02,400
Okay.

493
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:04,120
Thank you.

494
00:25:05,360 --> 00:25:06,120
Mr. Zhang.

495
00:25:06,840 --> 00:25:07,600
Thank you.

496
00:25:11,360 --> 00:25:12,820
You are riding a horse now.

497
00:25:15,800 --> 00:25:18,200
I asked for permission to practice riding.

498
00:25:26,240 --> 00:25:26,960
When I first came here,

499
00:25:26,960 --> 00:25:28,600
it was really eye-opening.

500
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:30,400
Commander Xie arranged for me

501
00:25:30,400 --> 00:25:31,640
to join the Civilian Training Class.

502
00:25:31,640 --> 00:25:34,080
My classmates were from all corners of the country,

503
00:25:34,080 --> 00:25:35,920
from college students who studied abroad

504
00:25:35,920 --> 00:25:37,320
to village girls like me.

505
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:38,600
We had classes together every day,

506
00:25:38,600 --> 00:25:39,440
lived together,

507
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,800
like a big family.

508
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:43,480
After three months of training,

509
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:44,440
I was assigned to

510
00:25:44,440 --> 00:25:45,440
the Civilian Movement Group of the Service Corps

511
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:46,600
to do civilian movement work.

512
00:25:46,600 --> 00:25:48,880
That was my first time wearing a military uniform

513
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:49,940
and a military cap.

514
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:51,760
I was so happy.

515
00:25:52,440 --> 00:25:54,120
There was a mirror in our Army Headquarters.

516
00:25:54,120 --> 00:25:56,160
We female soldiers rushed to look in it.

517
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:57,080
Then we said

518
00:25:57,360 --> 00:25:58,760
we would go to town together

519
00:25:58,760 --> 00:26:00,360
to find a photo studio to take a picture.

520
00:26:00,360 --> 00:26:01,440
The photographer

521
00:26:01,520 --> 00:26:04,560
kept calling me Comrade Han.

522
00:26:05,480 --> 00:26:07,760
Mr. Zhang, I'm Comrade Han now.

523
00:26:07,760 --> 00:26:09,040
Okay, Comrade Han.

524
00:26:09,240 --> 00:26:11,640
How exactly do you do civilian movement work?

525
00:26:11,640 --> 00:26:13,600
We were a group of five or six,

526
00:26:13,680 --> 00:26:15,840
men and women, forming a work group.

527
00:26:16,240 --> 00:26:18,040
One time when we entered a village,

528
00:26:18,040 --> 00:26:19,520
before we could even put down our backpacks,

529
00:26:19,520 --> 00:26:21,080
we were surrounded by a crowd.

530
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:21,960
Actually, they came to see

531
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:23,760
the female soldiers of the New Fourth Army.

532
00:26:23,760 --> 00:26:25,880
The common people have always been afraid of soldiers,

533
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:27,480
but the New Fourth Army has a good reputation.

534
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:29,040
We truly resist the Japanese and don't disturb the people.

535
00:26:29,040 --> 00:26:30,640
Since they dared to surround us,

536
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:33,000
we smiled and struck up a conversation with them.

537
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:35,040
At night, we paid for room and board

538
00:26:35,240 --> 00:26:36,680
and stayed in the farmers' homes.

539
00:26:36,680 --> 00:26:38,120
I helped the landlord

540
00:26:38,120 --> 00:26:39,680
sweep the floor, carry water,

541
00:26:39,680 --> 00:26:41,540
hold the baby, and wipe the table.

542
00:26:41,560 --> 00:26:43,620
At night, I stayed with the landlady,

543
00:26:43,840 --> 00:26:45,840
talking and chatting intimately.

544
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:48,360
During the day, we went out from door to door.

545
00:26:48,360 --> 00:26:49,360
Comrade Han, busy?

546
00:26:49,360 --> 00:26:50,240
You're here.

547
00:26:50,240 --> 00:26:50,800
Here.

548
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:52,040
Comrade Han.

549
00:26:53,280 --> 00:26:53,920
Comrade Han.

550
00:26:53,920 --> 00:26:55,040
Mr. Zhang, sit.

551
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:02,440
During the day, we went out to visit the poor and ask about their hardships,

552
00:27:02,440 --> 00:27:03,760
and show great concern for them.

553
00:27:03,760 --> 00:27:05,120
We went to people's homes

554
00:27:05,120 --> 00:27:06,640
to see if their rice vats were full.

555
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:09,320
Do they have chickens in the yard? Do they raise pigs?

556
00:27:09,320 --> 00:27:10,080
Think about it,

557
00:27:10,080 --> 00:27:11,760
raising chickens produces eggs.

558
00:27:11,760 --> 00:27:13,320
Then the women would have pocket money.

559
00:27:13,320 --> 00:27:14,080
With pocket money,

560
00:27:14,080 --> 00:27:16,740
they can buy a few books for the children to read.

561
00:27:17,280 --> 00:27:19,720
The important things that concern the farmers' vital interests

562
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:22,640
are the rice vat and the breeding of livestock and poultry.

563
00:27:22,640 --> 00:27:24,400
Like this year's Spring famine,

564
00:27:24,400 --> 00:27:26,330
many people's rice vats are empty.

565
00:27:26,520 --> 00:27:27,960
We organized

566
00:27:28,080 --> 00:27:29,680
to borrow grain from landlords

567
00:27:29,680 --> 00:27:31,720
and propose rent and interest reduction.

568
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:33,200
Before the Japanese came,

569
00:27:33,400 --> 00:27:34,930
we organized the villagers

570
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:38,000
to take food, pots, bowls,

571
00:27:38,040 --> 00:27:40,360
baskets, sacks, and other useful things,

572
00:27:40,360 --> 00:27:42,000
find a place to dig a hole and bury them.

573
00:27:42,000 --> 00:27:43,330
When the Japanese come,

574
00:27:43,480 --> 00:27:45,080
they will find nothing here.

575
00:27:45,080 --> 00:27:46,480
Not even a bite to eat.

576
00:27:46,960 --> 00:27:48,080
After hiding the things,

577
00:27:48,080 --> 00:27:50,080
we organized the villagers to flee.

578
00:27:50,280 --> 00:27:51,320
But

579
00:27:51,760 --> 00:27:53,160
what moved me the most

580
00:27:53,640 --> 00:27:54,900
was the fire-burners.

581
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:56,520
Fire-burners?

582
00:27:59,360 --> 00:28:00,760
As long as the Japanese come,

583
00:28:00,760 --> 00:28:02,890
the people burn down their own houses.

584
00:28:03,440 --> 00:28:04,440
When the Japanese leave,

585
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:05,840
they rebuild them.

586
00:28:06,200 --> 00:28:08,930
They just won't leave anything for the Japanese.

587
00:28:09,120 --> 00:28:10,040
Mr. Zhang,

588
00:28:10,520 --> 00:28:12,280
I see a kind of strength in them.

589
00:28:12,600 --> 00:28:14,040
With this strength,

590
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:17,160
our War of Resistance will definitely win.

591
00:28:20,280 --> 00:28:21,810
It's only been a few months,

592
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:24,920
you've been reborn and grown up.

593
00:28:26,400 --> 00:28:29,440
You ride horses and carry a gun.

594
00:28:31,280 --> 00:28:31,920
Our Civilian Movement Group

595
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:34,400
is going to Rudong area tomorrow to open up new areas.

596
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:35,200
Our Regimental Commander said

597
00:28:35,200 --> 00:28:36,720
the enemy situation there is complicated.

598
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:38,400
That's why I was issued a gun today.

599
00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:39,960
Do you know how to disassemble a gun?

600
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:41,360
I've used a Type 38 rifle,

601
00:28:41,560 --> 00:28:43,000
but I don't know how to disassemble this one yet.

602
00:28:43,000 --> 00:28:43,860
I'll teach you.

603
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:45,440
Okay.

604
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:48,920
Like this. First, press this.

605
00:28:49,120 --> 00:28:49,840
Look,

606
00:28:51,360 --> 00:28:52,120
it's off.

607
00:28:55,520 --> 00:28:56,680
Then hold this,

608
00:28:56,680 --> 00:28:58,800
push it forward and down,

609
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:00,760
and it comes off.

610
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:05,920
Assemble these three first.

611
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:06,680
Come on.

612
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:07,480
Okay.

613
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:13,240
Like this first.

614
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:15,120
Align it.

615
00:29:18,320 --> 00:29:19,040
Be careful.

616
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:23,760
How is it? Not slower than you, right?

617
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:28,720
Where did this come from?

618
00:29:28,720 --> 00:29:29,640
From inside the gun.

619
00:29:29,640 --> 00:29:31,000
Okay, I'll try again.

620
00:29:33,120 --> 00:29:35,160
Remove the magazine first.

621
00:29:36,280 --> 00:29:37,200
Then...

622
00:30:10,280 --> 00:30:11,160
Mrs. Ding, you're back.

623
00:30:11,160 --> 00:30:12,220
Slow down, Father.

624
00:30:13,560 --> 00:30:15,220
I just brought my father back.

625
00:30:15,240 --> 00:30:16,170
Come, slow down.

626
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:17,480
Do you need help?

627
00:30:17,480 --> 00:30:18,480
No, thank you.

628
00:30:18,880 --> 00:30:20,680
This is Mr. Jiang and Mrs. Jiang,

629
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:21,840
our neighbors.

630
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:22,680
Hello.

631
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:23,440
Hello.

632
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,120
You must be Mr. He.

633
00:30:26,120 --> 00:30:26,680
Let me do it.

634
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:27,800
No, thank you.

635
00:30:28,800 --> 00:30:30,680
Mr. He, you have no idea.

636
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:31,880
You were away these past few days.

637
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:32,480
Go play in the back room.

638
00:30:32,480 --> 00:30:33,280
Your wife has been busy

639
00:30:33,280 --> 00:30:33,840
managing everything here.

640
00:30:33,840 --> 00:30:34,640
Father, come.

641
00:30:35,160 --> 00:30:36,560
Your bed is in this room.

642
00:30:37,600 --> 00:30:38,860
Sit here and rest a bit.

643
00:30:39,320 --> 00:30:40,650
You married a good wife.

644
00:30:41,200 --> 00:30:42,800
Of course, we lent a hand too,

645
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,920
helping move some large furniture.

646
00:30:45,440 --> 00:30:47,040
A near neighbor is better than a distant cousin.

647
00:30:47,040 --> 00:30:48,800
Just let us know if you need anything in the future.

648
00:30:48,800 --> 00:30:49,400
Thank you.

649
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:52,130
The food is burning.

650
00:30:54,160 --> 00:30:54,960
Look at you.

651
00:31:09,640 --> 00:31:11,680
Who is it? So sneaky.

652
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:13,200
We live in this house.

653
00:31:13,440 --> 00:31:16,040
On the surface, Liao prepared it for us,

654
00:31:16,240 --> 00:31:19,560
but in reality, it was arranged by Lin Changgeng.

655
00:31:20,720 --> 00:31:22,200
Everyone living up and down this building

656
00:31:22,200 --> 00:31:24,260
are intelligence agents from No. 76,

657
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:26,640
including Section Chief Jiang and Mrs. Jiang just now.

658
00:31:26,640 --> 00:31:27,600
They are too.

659
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:31,360
This is Lin Changgeng placing

660
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:33,440
a pair of ears right next to our home.

661
00:31:36,040 --> 00:31:36,720
Wanfu.

662
00:31:37,360 --> 00:31:38,400
From now on,

663
00:31:39,120 --> 00:31:40,840
you are taking on the identity of Yunkui

664
00:31:40,840 --> 00:31:41,840
to act as He Bishi.

665
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:43,680
When dealing with them in the future,

666
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:46,280
remember to be cautious in speech and behavior,

667
00:31:46,280 --> 00:31:47,740
and be mature and prudent.

668
00:31:48,840 --> 00:31:49,760
And Master.

669
00:31:50,120 --> 00:31:52,560
Keep an eye on him and don't let him run out.

670
00:31:52,840 --> 00:31:55,400
Don't let him see so many Japanese and traitors

671
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:56,800
and get triggered again.

672
00:31:56,800 --> 00:31:57,680
Understood.

673
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:02,440
Yueming.

674
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:06,800
Intelligence just received:

675
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:08,440
The Japanese Army is inside the occupied zone

676
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:11,040
stepping up the construction of strongholds.

677
00:32:11,360 --> 00:32:13,020
It seems they will soon launch

678
00:32:13,040 --> 00:32:14,720
a large-scale mopping-up operation.

679
00:32:14,720 --> 00:32:16,520
The commanders are making plans

680
00:32:16,560 --> 00:32:19,720
to carry out flexible anti-mopping-up battles.

681
00:32:21,040 --> 00:32:22,960
Your appointment has also come down.

682
00:32:22,960 --> 00:32:23,720
Really?

683
00:32:25,480 --> 00:32:26,240
Where to?

684
00:32:26,840 --> 00:32:29,240
The higher-ups highly value your joining us,

685
00:32:29,240 --> 00:32:30,600
they also know your past,

686
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:32,400
and have high expectations of you.

687
00:32:32,400 --> 00:32:33,520
So they hope you

688
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:35,130
can return to Haiwen

689
00:32:35,520 --> 00:32:38,480
to continue organizing and leading the Haiwen Self-Defense Group.

690
00:32:38,480 --> 00:32:39,480
Go back to Haiwen?

691
00:32:39,520 --> 00:32:40,120
Yes.

692
00:32:40,400 --> 00:32:41,120
Yunkui.

693
00:32:41,600 --> 00:32:43,960
Ever since Wang's puppet government was established,

694
00:32:43,960 --> 00:32:45,420
some troops have defected

695
00:32:45,720 --> 00:32:46,920
to Wang's side.

696
00:32:47,280 --> 00:32:48,160
In other words,

697
00:32:48,280 --> 00:32:49,540
their next plan must be

698
00:32:49,800 --> 00:32:51,800
the big fish eat the small fish.

699
00:32:52,440 --> 00:32:54,560
To assimilate local stragglers,

700
00:32:54,760 --> 00:32:57,920
strengthen the puppet organization, and unify the puppet troops.

701
00:32:57,920 --> 00:32:59,520
According to the news we just received,

702
00:32:59,520 --> 00:33:00,380
over in Haiwen,

703
00:33:00,800 --> 00:33:04,360
Ge Zhiyuan officially defected to the puppet regime at the end of last month

704
00:33:04,360 --> 00:33:06,040
and was appointed as brigade commander.

705
00:33:06,040 --> 00:33:07,360
Only Ge Zhancheng

706
00:33:07,600 --> 00:33:08,720
and Magistrate Fan are left

707
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:09,980
struggling to hold on.

708
00:33:10,040 --> 00:33:11,240
Let me put it this way,

709
00:33:11,560 --> 00:33:14,040
the situation for the real resistance forces

710
00:33:14,040 --> 00:33:15,280
will only get worse from now on.

711
00:33:15,280 --> 00:33:17,360
On one hand, the New Fourth Army needs to carry out

712
00:33:17,360 --> 00:33:18,760
anti-mopping-up operations.

713
00:33:18,760 --> 00:33:19,760
On the other hand,

714
00:33:19,760 --> 00:33:21,840
we need to go deeper into the grassroots

715
00:33:21,840 --> 00:33:24,440
and develop local armed forces more covertly

716
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:27,080
to prevent the situation from worsening.

717
00:33:27,400 --> 00:33:28,600
So over in Haiwen,

718
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:31,000
they really need an expert like you.

719
00:33:32,120 --> 00:33:33,650
If I understand correctly,

720
00:33:34,200 --> 00:33:36,760
the designation of the Haiwen Self-Defense Group

721
00:33:36,760 --> 00:33:37,960
is a local armed force.

722
00:33:37,960 --> 00:33:38,760
That's right.

723
00:33:39,800 --> 00:33:41,080
The Haiwen Self-Defense Group

724
00:33:41,080 --> 00:33:43,610
will not use the banner of the New Fourth Army.

725
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:48,480
Yunkui,

726
00:33:49,600 --> 00:33:50,760
Haiwen

727
00:33:51,040 --> 00:33:53,160
enjoys an extremely advantageous geographical location.

728
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:54,760
It is along the river and close to the sea,

729
00:33:54,760 --> 00:33:56,960
with many docks and a dense population.

730
00:33:57,200 --> 00:33:58,200
It can be said that

731
00:33:58,760 --> 00:34:00,440
only by controlling Haiwen

732
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:02,400
can we ensure the transportation link

733
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:04,360
between Central Jiangsu and Jiangnan.

734
00:34:04,360 --> 00:34:06,960
Transporting and purchasing military supplies,

735
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:08,120
and covering the safe passage

736
00:34:08,120 --> 00:34:10,360
of our Party's political and military cadres,

737
00:34:10,360 --> 00:34:12,560
dealing with stubborn forces and local armed forces,

738
00:34:12,560 --> 00:34:13,880
and collecting intelligence on the Japanese Puppet Army

739
00:34:13,880 --> 00:34:16,120
are all tasks of the Haiwen Self-Defense Group.

740
00:34:16,120 --> 00:34:17,080
Yufeng,

741
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:18,639
may I ask a question?

742
00:34:19,080 --> 00:34:19,760
Please.

743
00:34:20,080 --> 00:34:22,679
Is letting me go back to Haiwen a test for me?

744
00:34:28,239 --> 00:34:29,440
To be exact,

745
00:34:30,040 --> 00:34:31,500
I think it should be trust.

746
00:34:32,440 --> 00:34:34,840
Yunkui, I don't know if you've thought about it.

747
00:34:34,840 --> 00:34:35,679
Letting you

748
00:34:36,199 --> 00:34:38,159
appear in a gray face

749
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:39,600
is actually more conducive

750
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:41,960
to your taking root in such a complex environment

751
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:45,000
with enemies, puppets, and stubborn forces.

752
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:46,560
The enemies

753
00:34:47,080 --> 00:34:49,360
want to ensure the safety of Yangtze River shipping

754
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:50,600
and plunder resources.

755
00:34:50,600 --> 00:34:51,730
Then the Haiwen area

756
00:34:51,840 --> 00:34:53,239
is bound to become an area

757
00:34:53,520 --> 00:34:55,760
where the struggle will become increasingly fierce.

758
00:34:55,760 --> 00:34:57,400
The superiors handed over such an important area

759
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:58,240
to you,

760
00:34:58,520 --> 00:35:01,000
which shows their level of trust.

761
00:35:01,760 --> 00:35:04,560
The Self-defense Group you developed in Yutang Town

762
00:35:04,560 --> 00:35:06,560
is actually a very good foundation.

763
00:35:06,840 --> 00:35:07,840
And I believe

764
00:35:08,280 --> 00:35:10,280
it will inevitably become a main force

765
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:11,740
of our Party in the future.

766
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:12,560
Of course,

767
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:14,420
the people you brought now

768
00:35:14,440 --> 00:35:16,320
can continue to complete their training here.

769
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:17,320
After you go back,

770
00:35:17,600 --> 00:35:18,800
I will send more hands

771
00:35:19,200 --> 00:35:21,040
to help you build the army

772
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:23,040
according to the standards of the New Fourth Army.

773
00:35:23,040 --> 00:35:25,360
You are indeed not the New Fourth Army in name,

774
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,480
but in fact,

775
00:35:26,720 --> 00:35:28,580
you are part of the New Fourth Army

776
00:35:28,960 --> 00:35:30,960
led by the Communist Party of China.

777
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:35,160
Understood. Resolutely execute the order.

778
00:35:37,480 --> 00:35:39,080
Commander, it's time to eat.

779
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:42,960
Yunkui, let's eat and talk.

780
00:35:42,960 --> 00:35:43,320
Okay.

781
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:43,920
Come.

782
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:48,930
Auntie Li, sit down.

783
00:35:50,880 --> 00:35:52,640
There's no good dish, just make do with it.

784
00:35:52,640 --> 00:35:53,000
Come.

785
00:35:53,200 --> 00:35:54,400
But to tell the truth,

786
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:55,360
this is already

787
00:35:55,360 --> 00:35:57,160
much better than the conditions

788
00:35:57,320 --> 00:35:59,440
when we fought guerrillas in Southwestern Jiangxi.

789
00:35:59,440 --> 00:36:00,170
At that time.

790
00:36:00,400 --> 00:36:00,880
Eat.

791
00:36:01,560 --> 00:36:04,560
We ate bitter vegetables and bamboo shoots every day.

792
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:06,280
Because of the blockade at that time,

793
00:36:06,280 --> 00:36:07,760
the common people couldn't go up.

794
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,160
Things like salt and rice

795
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:10,320
were not available at all.

796
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:12,240
It would be good to find some Suaeda salsa.

797
00:36:12,240 --> 00:36:13,480
There was no other way.

798
00:36:13,480 --> 00:36:15,680
We held on even in such poor conditions.

799
00:36:15,880 --> 00:36:17,840
Hardships are just like this.

800
00:36:18,080 --> 00:36:20,210
There are hardships today, tomorrow,

801
00:36:20,280 --> 00:36:21,080
and every day.

802
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:24,280
But fortunately we have now learned

803
00:36:24,520 --> 00:36:25,400
to live in peace

804
00:36:25,640 --> 00:36:26,680
with hardships.

805
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:28,000
Right?

806
00:36:28,160 --> 00:36:28,560
Yes.

807
00:36:28,720 --> 00:36:29,400
Eat up.

808
00:36:29,520 --> 00:36:30,080
Yes.

809
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:32,680
I'll take you for a walk by the river after you finish eating.

810
00:36:32,680 --> 00:36:33,320
Okay.

811
00:36:43,480 --> 00:36:44,360
Yueming,

812
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:46,320
you haven't seen your grandfather for over a year.

813
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:47,360
Did you miss me?

814
00:36:48,040 --> 00:36:48,520
Yes.

815
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:49,440
I did.

816
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:51,040
You've grown so tall.

817
00:36:51,320 --> 00:36:53,760
Do you think I've gained or lost weight?

818
00:36:54,520 --> 00:36:55,760
Lost weight.

819
00:37:18,040 --> 00:37:18,560
Father,

820
00:37:18,960 --> 00:37:19,600
careful, it's hot.

821
00:37:19,600 --> 00:37:20,530
Okay, come here.

822
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:23,560
Come, stir it for me.

823
00:37:24,040 --> 00:37:25,480
I'm not drinking.

824
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:29,880
Wanfu, eat something.

825
00:37:31,720 --> 00:37:32,880
It's egg drop soup.

826
00:37:34,680 --> 00:37:36,810
I've been craving this for over a year.

827
00:37:54,200 --> 00:37:56,360
I made this Baozi your way,

828
00:37:56,640 --> 00:37:57,900
with eighteen pleats.

829
00:37:58,680 --> 00:38:01,840
But the filling isn't as good as yours.

830
00:38:03,600 --> 00:38:06,840
It is said in the "Book of Songs - Major Odes - Han Yi".

831
00:38:07,760 --> 00:38:08,420
Delicious.

832
00:38:13,880 --> 00:38:14,680
What's wrong?

833
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:19,760
Forgot the sugar.

834
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:22,840
I couldn't even tell.

835
00:38:25,400 --> 00:38:26,730
Add some sugar, Father.

836
00:38:41,640 --> 00:38:43,160
You need to eat it while it's hot.

837
00:38:43,160 --> 00:38:43,480
Okay.

838
00:38:43,480 --> 00:38:45,210
It tastes fishy when it's cold.

839
00:38:45,240 --> 00:38:46,320
Come,

840
00:38:47,160 --> 00:38:48,820
Yueming, stir it for me again.

841
00:38:48,920 --> 00:38:49,720
Sugar's in.

842
00:38:50,800 --> 00:38:51,920
Stir.

843
00:38:52,600 --> 00:38:53,600
Is there any more?

844
00:38:54,680 --> 00:38:55,400
Yes.

845
00:39:23,000 --> 00:39:24,130
It's easy to imagine

846
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:26,640
how you've lived this past year.

847
00:39:28,040 --> 00:39:29,840
The food at home

848
00:39:30,480 --> 00:39:32,720
might not be the best, but

849
00:39:34,160 --> 00:39:35,690
we definitely have enough.

850
00:39:47,400 --> 00:39:48,200
I'm used to it.

851
00:39:49,400 --> 00:39:51,530
Always afraid Master would go hungry.

852
00:40:17,880 --> 00:40:18,610
Is it enough?

853
00:40:22,760 --> 00:40:23,440
Not quite.

854
00:40:25,240 --> 00:40:26,900
I'll go make you some noodles.

855
00:40:28,280 --> 00:40:29,410
I won't eat anymore.

856
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:31,010
Since I just got out,

857
00:40:31,200 --> 00:40:32,660
I'm afraid of overeating.

858
00:40:37,480 --> 00:40:38,120
Where

859
00:40:38,680 --> 00:40:39,440
do I sleep?

860
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:42,460
I have to ask you to bear with it

861
00:40:42,880 --> 00:40:45,160
and sleep on the floor next to Master.

862
00:40:46,080 --> 00:40:47,210
Okay, I'll set it up.

863
00:40:47,240 --> 00:40:48,160
Don't move.

864
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:49,720
You don't know where things are.

865
00:40:49,720 --> 00:40:50,440
Let me do it.

866
00:40:51,960 --> 00:40:53,840
Give me a hand to move the table.

867
00:40:53,920 --> 00:40:55,050
What are they doing?

868
00:40:55,160 --> 00:40:56,280
I don't know.

869
00:40:56,320 --> 00:40:57,080
Let me see.

870
00:41:04,320 --> 00:41:06,560
You and Yueming stay on the big bed for a bit.

871
00:41:06,560 --> 00:41:06,890
Okay.

872
00:41:06,920 --> 00:41:08,580
Come, Yueming, let me hug you.

873
00:41:08,640 --> 00:41:09,840
Hug.

874
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:11,010
Yueming,

875
00:41:11,080 --> 00:41:11,940
I'm not eating.

876
00:41:12,280 --> 00:41:13,740
I'm telling you, Yueming,

877
00:41:14,000 --> 00:41:15,200
I saw your drawing.

878
00:41:15,280 --> 00:41:16,120
Wait a moment.

879
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:17,160
Once this is set up,

880
00:41:17,160 --> 00:41:19,420
I'll get a towel for you to wipe your face.

881
00:41:20,080 --> 00:41:21,920
I'm bald in your drawing.

882
00:41:22,600 --> 00:41:23,520
I'm telling you,

883
00:41:23,520 --> 00:41:26,280
I brought your drawing back.

884
00:41:26,720 --> 00:41:27,120
Sit.

885
00:41:29,040 --> 00:41:29,800
Look at this.

886
00:41:30,800 --> 00:41:32,640
I've kept it all this time. Look.

887
00:41:33,640 --> 00:41:35,160
Yueming, sit properly.

888
00:41:36,240 --> 00:41:38,400
Look, it says right here.

889
00:41:38,720 --> 00:41:40,480
Yueming's home.

890
00:41:40,600 --> 00:41:42,880
Written by Yujiao.

891
00:41:43,520 --> 00:41:44,640
Then tell me,

892
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:46,040
who is this you drew?

893
00:41:46,040 --> 00:41:46,920
Grandpa.

894
00:41:47,080 --> 00:41:49,610
Grandpa? Why does Grandpa have so much beard?

895
00:41:50,560 --> 00:41:51,880
You don't have this much beard.

896
00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:52,880
Of course I don't.

897
00:41:53,160 --> 00:41:54,120
Then who is this?

898
00:41:54,200 --> 00:41:54,760
Yueming.

899
00:41:55,040 --> 00:41:55,720
Yueming.

900
00:41:56,080 --> 00:41:57,740
Then why are you a little ball?

901
00:41:58,960 --> 00:42:00,920
Why is Yueming a ball?

902
00:42:01,000 --> 00:42:02,130
Why is there one eye?

903
00:42:02,160 --> 00:42:03,040
Only one eye.

904
00:42:03,160 --> 00:42:04,560
Then tell me, who is this?

905
00:42:04,560 --> 00:42:05,120
Mom.

906
00:42:05,600 --> 00:42:07,040
Why does Mom have three eyes?

907
00:42:07,040 --> 00:42:08,040
Did Yueming give one of his eyes

908
00:42:08,040 --> 00:42:09,120
to Mom?

909
00:42:09,240 --> 00:42:09,800
Yes.

910
00:42:10,600 --> 00:42:12,000
Okay, now tell me,

911
00:42:12,040 --> 00:42:13,680
who is this bald guy you drew?

912
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:14,840
It's

913
00:42:16,680 --> 00:42:18,320
Dad.

914
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:33,800
Tell me,

915
00:42:35,400 --> 00:42:36,120
who is this?

916
00:42:36,200 --> 00:42:37,280
Dad.
